en.name: Fence figurine
en.description: The limited Tarko figurine is as mysterious as Fence himself.

en.name: Hardened PMC figurine
en.description: A Tarko figurine depicting a truly seasoned PMC operator who's been around for a while and seen some shit.

en.name: Mechanic figurine
en.description: Even in a Tarko figurine depiction, Mechanic remains a true weapons specialist.

en.name: Peacekeeper figurine
en.description: Even as a limited Tarko figurine, Peacekeeper seems ready to help and… no, nevermind, he's still just earning money for himself.

en.name: Skier figurine
en.description: The creator of this limited Tarko figurine clearly knows Skier well. Otherwise, how could they capture his character so perfectly?

en.name: Right half of a Physical Bitcoin
en.description: The right half of the physical equivalent of the Bitcoin cryptocurrency. It's unclear who decided to destroy an entire fortune and why.

en.name: Therapist figurine
en.description: This limited Tarko figurine depicts Therapist, ready to save a few unfortunate souls. Or take your money for questionable medical services.

en.name: Elvisvista figurine
en.description: The creator of this Tarko figurine depicted someone from the past, when life in Tarkov was calmer. It seems the person was an artist, but that's not certain.

en.name: Walking Tank figurine
en.description: A Tarko collectible figurine depicting an operative in a special loadout based on the advice from knowledgeable people. Please do not try this loadout at home.

en.name: BTR figurine
en.description: A collectible figurine from an unknown creator, showcasing the best means of transportation in all of Tarkov.

en.name: Ragman figurine
en.description: Even as a Tarko figurine, Ragman looks every bit the true businessman.

en.name: Left half of a Physical Bitcoin
en.description: The left half of the physical equivalent of the Bitcoin cryptocurrency. It's unclear who decided to destroy an entire fortune and why.

en.name: Jaeger figurine
en.description: The creator of this figurine captured Jaeger with incredible precision, even conveying the depth of emotion in his eyes.

en.name: Ref figurine
en.description: The figurine Ref looks just like the real one, always on the lookout for new fighters for the Arena.

en.name: Hideout Cat figurine
en.description: This cat was destined to become part of the Tarko figurine collection.

en.name: Lightkeeper figurine
en.description: This limited Tarko figurine shows Tarkov’s Gray Cardinal. Some people know what Lightkeeper looks like only thanks to this figurine.

en.name: Escape figurine
en.description: A Tarko collectible figurine depicting a PMC operative who went through fire, water and copper pipes.

en.name: Mastichin figurine
en.description: A limited Tarko figurine depicting a Tarkov resident.

en.name: Prapor figurine
en.description: This limited Tarko figurine shows Prapor in his best mood.
